; &agrave; un utilisateur mais ne prennent pas en compte les&nbsp;custom post type. Ce tutoriel vous montrera comment g&eacute;n&eacute;rer des pages d&rsquo;archives de l&rsquo;auteur incluant tous les contenus r&eacute;dig&eacute;s. Pour rappel, chaque auteur dispose d&rsquo;un URL qui lui est propre. Par exemple, vous pouvez retrouver les articles ...</p>\n<p><a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpchannel.com/author/aurelien-denis/">Aur&eacute;lien Denis</a> - <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpchannel.com/">WordPress Channel - Tutoriels, th&egrave;mes &amp; plugins WordPress</a> - <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="http://wpchannel.com/custom-post-types-pages-auteurs-wordpress/">Afficher les custom post types dans les pages auteurs de WordPress</a>	\n<a rel="nofollow" title="Th&egrave;mes premiums pour WordPress" target="_blank" href="http://wpchannel.com/go/elegant-themes.php"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-12230" title="elegant-themes-large" src="http://wpchannel.com/images/2010/09/elegant-themes-large.jpg" alt="" width="570" height="100"></a></p>\n</div>";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:68:"\n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n        \n    ";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:72:"GeekPress : Empêcher l’usurpation l’identité dans les commentaires";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:4:"type";s:4:"html";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:2:"id";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:88:"http://www.geekpress.fr/wordpress/astuce/empecher-usurpation-identite-commentaires-1476/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s: